com.here.android.mpa.ar

Class ARController.IntroAnimationParams

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.ar.ARController.IntroAnimationParams
  • Enclosing class:
    ARController

    public final class ARController.IntroAnimationParams
extends java.lang.Object
    Encapsulates parameters which affect the Intro Animation. The Intro Animation refers to the animation that is performed right after calling ARController.start().
